  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200&deg;C/ 180&deg;C (fan)/ 400&deg;F/ Gas 6</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>quinoa</strong> to a pot with a matching lid, with 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span><strong> cold water</strong>&nbsp;<span class=\"text-highlight\">&amp;</span> bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low <span class=\"text-highlight\">&amp;</span> cook, covered, for <span class=\"text-highlight\">18-20 min</span> or until all the water has absorbed <span class=\"text-highlight\">&amp;</span> the quinoa is tender</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, remove from the heat <span class=\"text-highlight\">&amp;</span> leave to steam-dry <span class=\"text-highlight\">until cool</span></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1145.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1145.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1145.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1145.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1145.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>feta</strong> to an oiled baking tray</p>\r\n<p>Drizzle with the <strong>honey </strong>and sprinkle with both the <strong>toasted</strong> and <strong>black sesame seeds&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min or until the feta is starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1145.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1145.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
